#Replace null values with 'Unknown' category and dug related tests as zero, job attributes with zero 
recidivismData['Gang_Affiliated'] = recidivismData['Gang_Affiliated'].fillna('Unknown')
recidivismData['Supervision_Risk_Score_First'] = recidivismData['Supervision_Risk_Score_First'].fillna(0)
recidivismData['Supervision_Level_First'] = recidivismData['Supervision_Level_First'].fillna('Unknown')
recidivismData['Prison_Offense'] = recidivismData['Prison_Offense'].fillna('Unknown')
recidivismData['Avg_Days_per_DrugTest'] = recidivismData['Avg_Days_per_DrugTest'].fillna(0)
recidivismData['DrugTests_THC_Positive'] = recidivismData['DrugTests_THC_Positive'].fillna(0)
recidivismData['DrugTests_Cocaine_Positive'] = recidivismData['DrugTests_Cocaine_Positive'].fillna(0)
recidivismData['DrugTests_Meth_Positive'] = recidivismData['DrugTests_Meth_Positive'].fillna(0)
recidivismData['DrugTests_Other_Positive'] = recidivismData['DrugTests_Other_Positive'].fillna(0)
recidivismData['Percent_Days_Employed'] = recidivismData['Percent_Days_Employed'].fillna(0)
recidivismData['Jobs_Per_Year'] = recidivismData['Jobs_Per_Year'].fillna(0)

In [410]:
#new column for future recidivism with 0 being no recidivism and 1-3 meaning the year
recidivismData['Future_Recidivism'] = recidivismData.apply(
    lambda row: 0 if row.Recidivism_Within_3years == False else (1 if row.Recidivism_Arrest_Year1 == True else (2 if row.Recidivism_Arrest_Year2 == True else 3)), axis=1)
